APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2006-0540. Zappitelli v. Miller.

Cuyahoga App. No. 85895, 2006-Ohio-279. Discretionary appeal accepted on Proposition of Law No. I.

Lanzinger, J., would also accept the appeal on all other Propositions of Law. Resnick, Pfeifer and O’Donnell, JJ., dissent.

Discretionary cross-appeal not accepted.
